        <TextBlock Margin="0,10" TextWrapping="Wrap">
			By Clicking 'Next' and proceeding with the installation, you imply agreement with the EULA as stated above. 
            If you do not agree, click 'Back' and then 'Cancel'.
        </TextBlock>
    </StackPanel>

</UserControl>
